reviewText: It had missing parts and it honestly disappointed me because there were some important parts in the original version on tv
Mi Pecado is one of the best novelas ive seen! I was realy surprised to see the dvd did a pretty good job editing!! i recommend this one!!!

I was so hapy when i saw that it was on DVD. It is such a great novela, and now i can watch it any time. It unfortuantly doesnt have the whole novela, but the parts that they cut out weren't really important. In my opinion it is the best.
